improved_metadata.title: Dust on the Keys (Cowboy on a Beat)
improved_metadata.description: A raw and honest song about finding solace and expression through music despite life's hardships, blending country and hip-hop influences. It paints a picture of rural life, struggle, and the power of storytelling.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Bust on the keys, yeah, bust on the keys
